            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1248724</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">支付宝在开放日活动中宣布全新付费方式「碰一下支付」。相比传统的「扫一下支付」，「碰一下支付」更加方便快捷，用户只需解锁手机并碰一下收款装置，即可完成付费，无需进入支付宝 App 点击付款码。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248726 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-3-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-3-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用户只需解锁手机并碰一下收款装置，即可完成付费（图片来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/780/382.htm?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2wx7IO9r43DKqLnxzV1t2xOII8QoCML7n6HMx-RzAqX47xXCSMFiVI1jU_aem_BVI-MlwwQI55YMXDOCCgxQ">IT 之家</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「碰一下支付」利用了手机的 NFC 技术，在手机解锁和 NFC 开启状态下，只需将手机靠近付费装置，即可自动跳转至确认页面，完成付费。过程省去传统「扫一下支付」所需的多个步骤。付费装置分为手持和枱式两种造型，适用于不同店铺的需求，并内置 4G 网络，无需依赖 Wi-Fi。「碰一下支付」兼容适配了包括鸿蒙、Android、iOS 在内的多种系统，亦支援银行卡、支付宝余额、余额宝、花呗、小荷包等多种付费方式。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248727 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-4-694x556.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="556" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-4-694x556.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-4.jpg 1123w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248734 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-5-684x580.jpg" alt="" width="684" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-5-684x580.jpg 684w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-5.jpg 1061w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 684px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「碰一下支付」已在全国多个地方使用（图片来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/780/382.htm?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2wx7IO9r43DKqLnxzV1t2xOII8QoCML7n6HMx-RzAqX47xXCSMFiVI1jU_aem_BVI-MlwwQI55YMXDOCCgxQ">IT 之家</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「碰一下支付」已经在上海、成都、武汉、长沙、杭州、福州等六个城市的超过 2300 个品牌及商家中试行，包括红旗、美宜佳、7-11、十足、逸刻、良品铺子等便利店，以及大型商场及社区，如上海静安大悦城、成都万象城、龙湖杭州滨江天街等。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/780/382.htm?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2wx7IO9r43DKqLnxzV1t2xOII8QoCML7n6HMx-RzAqX47xXCSMFiVI1jU_aem_BVI-MlwwQI55YMXDOCCgxQ">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/07/sams-club-to-hongkong/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国山姆超市今日起可直送香港　现接受 Alipay HK、支付宝、微信支付</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/alipay-3/fun-tech/">支付宝推 NFC「碰一下支付」     全中国超过 2300 个品牌试行</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
