            <title>易通行系统周一网络不稳，受影响车辆数目待确认</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/hketoll-9/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hketoll-9</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/hketoll-9/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:00:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[易通行]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[运输署]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1248717</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">易通行系统于周一（</span>8 <span lang="ZH-TW">日</span><span lang="ZH-TW">）下午出现网络不稳定情况，导致部分服务运作受影响，现已回复正常，</span><span lang="ZH-TW">惟</span><span lang="ZH-TW">受影响车辆数目仍待确认。</span></p></div><div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1248719 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-694x432.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="432" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at-694x432.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240709at.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲<span lang="ZH-TW">易通行服务商于周一中午 </span>12 <span lang="ZH-TW">时左右发现系统网络不稳，导致部分服务运作受影响（图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1728926-20231122.htm">RTHK</a>）</span></p></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">运输署表示，易通行服务商于周一中午 </span>12 <span lang="ZH-TW">时左右发现系统网络不稳，影响部分用户登入及接收系统通知。有驾驶人士反映，在 </span>1 <span lang="ZH-TW">分钟内被扣款两次，部分用户在登入易通行手机应用程式或网页时遇到延误或需重新登入的问题。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">有</span><span lang="ZH-TW">受影响人士反映，于周一下午 </span>2 <span lang="ZH-TW">时收到信用卡扣款通知，显示其车辆在 </span>1 <span lang="ZH-TW">分钟内进出香港仔隧道时被扣款两次。运输署发言人指，系统于周一下午 </span>4 <span lang="ZH-TW">时已回复正常，并强调事件不涉及网络攻击，服务商已立即进行紧急检查及跟进，并持续进行网络及系统维护。</span></p></div><div></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">运输署已要求服务商提交详细报告，并会共同研究改善措施。受影响用户可联络易通行 </span>24 <span lang="ZH-TW">小时客户服务热线查询有关情况及款项处理事宜。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">有明报</span><span lang="ZH-TW">读者反映，周一下午 </span>4 <span lang="ZH-TW">时及 </span>6 <span lang="ZH-TW">时两次致电易通行热线时，获告知系统正在更新中，职员建议稍后再登入查看。</span></p></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1728926-20231122.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://life.mingpao.com/general/article?issue=20240709&amp;nodeid=1720462317709">明报</a>、<a href="https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=567467&amp;fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR32PIVrMIA2T-cJC5p5VsDeBdkdF49Nsy3iQsbVPIAyjht5TEghbD-X4Os_aem_sgKAMij96BxGMcFST23q7A">Now 新闻</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/06/hketoll-8/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">林世雄：易通行实施近一年，红隧繁忙时段车龙减少超过 1 公里</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/09/hketoll-9/life-tech/smartcity/">易通行系统周一网络不稳，受影响车辆数目待确认</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
